Regent Model
Copyright (c) 2026 Alchymia AI Research Labs

This product is developed and maintained by Alchymia AI Research Labs.

The Regent Model is a hybrid Mamba-2 language model with a dual-head
architecture for built-in hallucination mitigation. It is designed for
the Grande Regent synthetic sentient runtime and related Alchymia AI
research initiatives.

All source code, model architectures, training pipelines, configurations,
documentation, presentations, and website materials in this repository
are the proprietary work of Alchymia AI Research Labs.

